---
import SectionHeader from '../common/SectionHeader.astro';
import Icon from '../common/Icon.astro';

const reveal = 'opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition duration-700 ease-out';
---

<section id="instalaciones" class="py-24">
  <SectionHeader title="El Laboratorio" tag="SEC: 02" />

  <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article data-reveal class={`${reveal} group relative overflow-hidden border border-black/10 bg-nasa-surface p-0 md:col-span-2`}>
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486262715619-67b85e0b08d3?q=80&w=2000&auto=format&fit=crop"
        alt="Detalle de motor en laboratorio"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover opacity-60 grayscale mix-blend-multiply transition duration-700 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:grayscale-0"
      />
      <div class="relative z-10 flex min-h-[22rem] flex-col justify-end bg-linear-to-t from-white/95 via-white/70 to-transparent p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-nasa-accent animate-pulse-soft"></span>
          <p class="m-0 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-black/70">Camara 01 // Area Limpia</p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="m-0 font-display text-2xl font-bold uppercase md:text-3xl">Sala de Control Principal</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.16em] text-nasa-accent">ENTORNO CONTROLADO / ISO CLASE 7</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal style="transition-delay:120ms" class={`${reveal} flex flex-col justify-between border border-nasa-accent bg-nasa-accent p-8 text-white`}>
      <Icon name="cpu" class="mb-8 size-12" />
      <div>
        <h3 class="m-0 font-display text-2xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight">
          Tecnologia
          <br />
          Propietaria
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 mb-0 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed font-medium text-white/90">
          Equipamiento de diagnostico de ultima generacion, superior a los estandares de concesionarios oficiales. Herramientas calibradas mensualmente.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal style="transition-delay:220ms" class={`${reveal} border border-black/10 bg-nasa-surface p-8`}>
      <Icon name="gauge" class="mb-4 size-8 text-nasa-accent" />
      <div class="mb-2 font-display text-5xl font-bold">99.9%</div>
      <p class="m-0 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-black/50">Tasa de precision en diagnostico inicial</p>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal class={`${reveal} border border-black/10 bg-nasa-surface p-8 md:col-span-2`}>
      <h3 class="mb-2 font-display text-xl font-bold uppercase">Transparencia Absoluta</h3>
      <p class="m-0 max-w-3xl font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed font-medium text-black/60">
        Recibe un reporte digital interactivo con fotografias, lecturas de sensores y explicaciones detalladas antes de autorizar cualquier procedimiento. Tu tienes el control total de la consola.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
